        },
        {
          "text": "lymphoma",
          "url": "https://wikem.org/wiki/Lymphoma"
        }
      ]
    },
    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Abdominal pain\nChronic\nnausea\n,\nvomiting\n,\ndiarrhea\nWeakness\nand fatigue\nSalt craving\nAbnormal skin pigmentation - will often look patchy\nAddisonian crisis:\nHypotension\nNeurologic symptoms:\ncoma",
      "subsections": {},
