    "Differential_Diagnosis": {
      "text": "Corticosteroid\nwithdrawal\nSecondary adrenal insufficiency - deficiency of ACTH (produced by the pituitary gland)\nTertiary adrenal insufficiency - deficiency of CRH (produced by the hypothalamus)",
